reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very important piece of my travel kit!!
reviews.reviewText: This is perfect for hang drying lightweight clothes while traveling. I used it to hang under garments and my daughter's compression stockings. For heavy things like pants and tops I used a plastic hanger over the shower bar. It easily attached from the shower head to the opposite end of the shower bar, wrapping the bungy cord end around the bar and back into itself to secure it. Perfect. Fits back in the included fabric bag! Quality item. Won't travel without it now.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good quality but heavy to pack
reviews.reviewText: This is a very good quality product. I used it for international travel and found it was too heavy for my preferences. The clips are coated metal. I think it would be excellent for RV camping or other situations where weight is not so significant.
